.pl?dn=db_musica_bios_pt&sn=musica&orn=516|title=Zolt\u00e1n Pesk\u00f3 (Maestro Titular)|accessdate=April 30, 2013|language=pt}}</ref><ref name=\"Who\" />\n\nZolt\u00e1n Pesk\u00f3 died in Budapest on 31 March 2020 at age of 83.<ref name=\"Scala\" /><ref name=\"WZ\" /><ref>[https://fidelio.hu/klasszikus/elhunyt-pesko-zoltan-vilaghiru-magyar-karmester-154174.html Elhunyt Pesk\u00f3 Zolt\u00e1n vil\u00e1gh\u00edr\u0171 magyar karmester] {{in lang|hu}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist\n| refs =\n\n<ref name=\"Scala\">{{cite web\n| url = https://www.connessiallopera.it/news/2020/zoltan-pesko-il-teatro-alla-scala-ricorda-il-direttore-scomparso/\n| title = Zolt\u00e1n Pesk\u00f3: il Teatro alla Scala ricorda il direttore scomparso\n| website = [[La Scala]]\n| date = 1 April 2020\n| language = it\n| accessdate = 2 April 2020\n}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Who\">{{cite web\n| url = http://www.whoswho.de/bio/zoltn-pesk.html\n| title = Zolt\u00e1n Pesk\u00f3\n| website = whoswho.de\n| date = \n| language = de\n| accessdate = 2 April 2020\n}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"WZ\">{{cite news\n| url = https://www.wienerzeitung.at/nachrichten/kultur/klassik/2056274-Dirigent-Zoltan-Pesko-gestorben.html\n| title = Dirigent Zoltan Pesko gestorben / Der ungarische Komponist verstarb im Alter von 83 Jahren.\n| newspaper = [[Wiener Zeitung]]\n| date = 1 April 2020\n| language = de\n| accessdate = 2 April 2020\n}}</ref>\n\n}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{commonscat}}\n* {{DNB portal|134483022}}\n* {{AllMusic|id=mn0001646354}}\n* {{IMDb name|nm0676016/}}\n* {{discogs artist}}\n* [https://de.schott-music.com/shop/autoren/zoltan-pesko Zolt\u00e1n Pesk\u00f3] Schott Music\n* [https://www.naxos.com/person/Zoltan_Pesko/53868.htm Zolt\u00e1n Pesk\u00f3] Naxos Records\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Pesko, Zoltan}}\n[[Category:1937 births]]\n[[Category:2020 deaths]]\n[[Category:Hungarian conductors (music)]]\n[[Category:Musicians from Budapest]]\n[[Category:21st-century conductors (music)]]\n\n\n{{Hu